"title": "5962: surprises",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5962",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>People are often taken unawares by God's power, love and wisdom. The actions of God and Jesus Christ are often described as surprising those who witnessed them.</p>\n<h2>God's actions surprise people</h2>\n<h3>Surprise at the sudden appearance of angels</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke1:11-Luke1:12\">LUK 1:11–1:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan8:16-Dan8:17\">DAN 8:16–8:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke1:28-Luke1:29\">LUK 1:28–1:29</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke2:9\">LUK 2:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts10:3-Acts10:4\">ACT 10:3–10:4</a></p>\n<h3>Surprise deliverance</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan3:26-Dan3:27\">DAN 3:26–3:27</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts5:19-Acts5:24\">ACT 5:19–5:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts12:14-Acts12:18\">ACT 12:14–12:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts28:6\">ACT 28:6</a></p>\n<h3>Surprise at special births</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke1:29-Luke1:34\">LUK 1:29–1:34</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen17:17\">GEN 17:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke1:18\">LUK 1:18</a></p>\n<h3>Surprise at the circumstances of Jesus Christ's death</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt27:54\">MAT 27:54</a></strong></p>\n<h3>Surprise at the coming of the Holy Spirit</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts2:6-Acts2:7\">ACT 2:6–2:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts10:45\">ACT 10:45</a></p>\n<h3>Surprise at the change in people's lives</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts9:21\">ACT 9:21</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark5:15\">MRK 5:15</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke8:35\">LUK 8:35</a></p>\n<h3>Surprise at the second coming</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt24:44\">MAT 24:44</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke12:40\">LUK 12:40</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mal3:1\">MAL 3:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt24:50\">MAT 24:50</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke12:46\">LUK 12:46</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt25:6\">MAT 25:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt25:13\">MAT 25:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark13:36\">MRK 13:36</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke21:34\">LUK 21:34</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess5:4\">1TH 5:4</a></p>\n<h3>Surprise at discernment</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt25:37-Matt25:39\">MAT 25:37–25:39</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt25:44\">MAT 25:44</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke5:22\">LUK 5:22</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John4:19\">JHN 4:19</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts5:5\">ACT 5:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts5:11\">ACT 5:11</a></p>\n<h2>Jesus Christ surprised people</h2>\n<h3>Surprise at Jesus Christ's moral requirements</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt5:20\">MAT 5:20</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt5:48\">MAT 5:48</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt18:21-Matt18:22\">MAT 18:21–18:22</a></p>\n<h3>Surprise at Jesus Christ's humility</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John13:6\">JHN 13:6</a></strong></p>\n<h3>Surprise at Jesus Christ's control of natural elements</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt8:27\">MAT 8:27</a></strong> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark4:41\">MRK 4:41</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke8:25\">LUK 8:25</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt14:25-Matt14:26\">MAT 14:25–14:26</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark6:49-Mark6:50\">MRK 6:49–6:50</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt21:20\">MAT 21:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke5:9\">LUK 5:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John2:8-John2:10\">JHN 2:8–2:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John6:14\">JHN 6:14</a></p>\n<h3>Surprise at the company Jesus Christ kept</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark2:16\">MRK 2:16</a></strong> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt9:11\">MAT 9:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke5:30\">LUK 5:30</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke7:39\">LUK 7:39</a></p>\n<h3>Surprise at Jesus Christ's healings</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark7:37\">MRK 7:37</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt9:6-Matt9:8\">MAT 9:6–9:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt9:33\">MAT 9:33</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt15:31\">MAT 15:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark5:42\">MRK 5:42</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke8:56\">LUK 8:56</a></p>\n<h3>Surprise at the requirements for entry into the kingdom of heaven</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt19:13-Matt19:15\">MAT 19:13–19:15</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark10:13-Mark10:16\">MRK 10:13–10:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke18:15-Luke18:17\">LUK 18:15–18:17</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt19:24-Matt19:25\">MAT 19:24–19:25</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark10:23-Mark10:26\">MRK 10:23–10:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke18:25-Luke18:26\">LUK 18:25–18:26</a></p>\n<h3>Surprise at Jesus Christ's teaching authority</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark1:22\">MRK 1:22</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke4:32\">LUK 4:32</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt7:28-Matt7:29\">MAT 7:28–7:29</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt22:33\">MAT 22:33</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark6:2-Mark6:4\">MRK 6:2–6:4</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt13:53-Matt13:54\">MAT 13:53–13:54</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark11:18\">MRK 11:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John7:15\">JHN 7:15</a></p>\n<h3>Surprise at the wisdom of Jesus Christ</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt22:22\">MAT 22:22</a></strong> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark12:17\">MRK 12:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke20:26\">LUK 20:26</a></p>\n<h3>Surprise at the expectations of Jesus Christ</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt14:16-Matt14:17\">MAT 14:16–14:17</a></strong> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark6:37\">MRK 6:37</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke9:13\">LUK 9:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John6:7-John6:9\">JHN 6:7–6:9</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt15:33-Matt15:36\">MAT 15:33–15:36</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark8:4-Mark8:6\">MRK 8:4–8:6</a></p>\n<h3>Surprise at Jesus Christ's authority in the spiritual realm</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark1:27\">MRK 1:27</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke4:36\">LUK 4:36</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark5:15-Mark5:17\">MRK 5:15–5:17</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt8:33-Matt8:34\">MAT 8:33–8:34</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke8:35-Luke8:37\">LUK 8:35–8:37</a></p>\n<h3>Surprise at Jesus Christ's disregard for Jewish customs</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke11:38\">LUK 11:38</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark7:5\">MRK 7:5</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt15:2\">MAT 15:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John4:27\">JHN 4:27</a></p>\n<h3>Surprise at Jesus Christ's rejection of religious words and actions</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt7:21-Matt7:23\">MAT 7:21–7:23</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke13:26-Luke13:27\">LUK 13:26–13:27</a></p>\n<h3>Surprise at Jesus Christ bringing back the dead</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke7:14-Luke7:16\">LUK 7:14–7:16</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark5:42\">MRK 5:42</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke8:56\">LUK 8:56</a></p>\n<h3>Surprise at the post-resurrection appearance of Jesus Christ</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke24:36-Luke24:37\">LUK 24:36–24:37</a></strong></p>\n<h2>Jesus Christ is surprised by people's reactions</h2>\n<h3>By the great faith of an unlikely person</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt8:10\">MAT 8:10</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke7:9\">LUK 7:9</a></p>\n<h3>By lack of faith among God's people</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark6:4-Mark6:6\">MRK 6:4–6:6</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt13:57-Matt13:58\">MAT 13:57–13:58</a></p>\n<h3>By the dullness of his followers</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt15:16\">MAT 15:16</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark7:18\">MRK 7:18</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt16:9-Matt16:11\">MAT 16:9–16:11</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark8:17-Mark8:18\">MRK 8:17–8:18</a></p>\n<h3>By lack of spiritual insight</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:9\">JHN 14:9</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John3:10\">JHN 3:10</a></p>\n<h2>Surprises for believers</h2>\n<h3>Surprise at suffering</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet4:12\">1PE 4:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John3:13\">1JN 3:13</a></p>\n<h3>Surprise at divine revelation</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke24:32\">LUK 24:32</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts10:17\">ACT 10:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts11:15\">ACT 11:15</a></p>\n<h2>Surprises caused by believers</h2>\n<h3>Surprising courage</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts4:13\">ACT 4:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan3:13\">DAN 3:13</a></p>\n<h3>Surprise at miracles</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts3:11-Acts3:12\">ACT 3:11–3:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts8:13\">ACT 8:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts14:11\">ACT 14:11</a></p>\n<h3>Surprise at the teaching about Jesus Christ</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts13:12\">ACT 13:12</a></p>",
